                    over to <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> the finished book of the <foreign xml:lang="gez">Taʾammǝra Māryām</foreign>, which she blesses and returns to him;  second, 
                    <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> presenting to <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/> a throne and garment; and third, Hildephonsus of Toledo's 
                    successor falling and being smitten by an <term key="angel">angel</term> for having touched Mary's gifts to Hildephonsus without 
